name: Vintage Flower Drop Earrings - Glass (Multiple colors)
description:
These Vintage Flower Drop Earrings are set on sterling silver threads that thread through the ear and worn at any length

Size: Total length of thread is 4 inches (when threaded the standard hanging length is 2 inches)

Materials: Vintage Glass set on Sterling Silver

These earrings are made with high grade Sterling Silver so no chance of irritation to your ears :-)

Color options: Yellow, Red, Grape, Blue, Turquoise

** I am constantly asked... How does it go through your ear?... the end of the chain is a hard post like any other post earring. Once that is in your ear, the chain (which is the same gauge as the post) is pulled through to the desired length. They are fabulous and fun... you will get many compliments;-)

See the model photo for the result!
